    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the pepper is in the oven, grate your <strong>cheddar cheese</strong></p><p>Drain your <strong>mozzarella</strong>, then pat and squeeze as much liquid out as you can with kitchen paper</p><p>Tear the <strong>drained mozzarella</strong> into rough, bite-sized pieces</p><p>Peel your <strong>garlic</strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
