    {
      "instruction": "<p>Wash your <strong>salad</strong> and pat it dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Combine<strong> half</strong> your <strong>pomegranate molasses</strong> in a bowl with <strong>half</strong> your <strong>white wine vinegar</strong> (you'll use the rest later!) and a generous drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>– this is your <strong>pomegranate dressing</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
