      "instruction": "<p>Add the<strong> peeled garlic</strong>,<strong> half </strong>your<strong> chilli flakes </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!),<strong> walnuts</strong>,<strong> ground cumin </strong>and<strong> ground smoked paprika </strong>to a <strong>food processor </strong>with the <strong>remaining pomegranate molasses </strong>and<strong> white wine vinegar</strong></p><p>Add 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp] </span><strong>olive oil</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and blitz  – this is your <strong>muhammara base</strong></p>",
